  "prompt": "Who is the best keyboardist on BITS, Pilani Campus?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" keyboardist at BITS Pilani Campus is quite subjective and can vary based on personal preferences, the style of music, and specific performances. BITS Pilani has a vibrant community with many talented musicians who contribute to various cultural and technical events.\n\nIf you're looking to identify standout keyboardists on campus, here are a few suggestions:\n\n1. **Campus Events and Competitions:** Keep an eye on performances during annual events like Festember, Technophilia, or other cultural fests. These events often showcase some of the most skilled musicians.\n\n2. **Music Clubs and Bands:** BITS Pilani hosts several music clubs and bands. Joining or attending their rehearsals and performances can help you discover talented keyboardists.\n\n3. **Social Media and Campus Forums:** Check out campus-specific social media groups, forums, or bulletin boards where students might share their performances or recommend fellow musicians.\n\n4. **Collaborate and Network:** Engaging with the music community on campus can provide insights and personal recommendations about who excels in keyboard playing.\n\nRemember, \"best\" can mean different things to different people\u2014whether it's technical skill, creativity, stage presence, or the ability to collaborate effectively. Exploring these avenues will give you a better sense of the talented keyboardists at BITS Pilani.",
